| test  | idx        | test        | t1         | NULL           | NULL              | INDEX       |      100 |
| test  | idx1_t1    | test        | t1         | NULL           | NULL              | INDEX       |      100 |
| test  | idx2_t1    | test        | t1         | NULL           | NULL              | INDEX       |      100 |
